VEd Ulbrich: That was a clip from "The Curious Case of Benjamin Button."
p42
aVMany of you, maybe you've seen it or you've heard of the story,
p43
aVbut what you might not know
p44
aVis that for nearly the first hour of the film,
p45
aVthe main character, Benjamin Button, who's played by Brad Pitt,
p46
aVis completely computer-generated from the neck up.
p47
aVNow, there's no use of prosthetic makeup
p48
aVor photography of Brad superimposed over another actor's body.
p49
aVWe've created a completely digital human head.
