aa(lp323
VNext we had to go into the shooting process.
p324
aVSo while all that's going on,
p325
aVwe're down in New Orleans and locations around the world.
p326
aVAnd we shot our body actors,
p327
aVand we shot them wearing blue hoods.
p328
aVSo these are the gentleman who played Benjamin.
p329
aVAnd the blue hoods helped us with two things:
p330
aVone, we could easily erase their heads;
p331
aVand we also put tracking markers on their heads
p332
aVso we could recreate the camera motion
p333
aVand the lens optics from the set.
