aa(lp335
VBut now we needed to get Brad's performance to drive our virtual Benjamin.
p336
aVAnd so we edited the footage that was shot on location
p337
aVwith the rest of the cast and the body actors
p338
aVand about six months later
p339
aVwe brought Brad onto a sound stage in Los Angeles
p340
aVand he watched on the screen.
p341
aVHis job, then, was to become Benjamin.
p342
aVAnd so we looped the scenes.
p343
aVHe watched again and again.
p344
aVWe encouraged him to improvise.
p345
aVAnd he took Benjamin into interesting and unusual places
p346
aVthat we didn't think he was going to go.
p347
aVWe shot him with four HD cameras
p348
aVso we'd get multiple views of him
p349
aVand then David would choose the take of Brad being Benjamin
p350
aVthat he thought best matched the footage
p351
aVwith the rest of the cast.
